<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>114</hymn_number>
<title>AMAH KA DAWT CH114</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka lung in vawlei sunpar a lo dih, Phannak in Jesuh thi nih a ka
 khamh, Vailamtahnak tang ah ka lungthin cu, Jesuh thi nih hawhra bangin a
 tawl dih cang.

[C1]
   Ka dawt ko, ka dawt ko, A ka dawt hmasa i Kalvary thingcung in a ka
   tlanh cang ca ah.

[V2]
 Sualnak ramlak chungah ka rak tlau cang, Ka lungchung duhnak sal kha
 ka rak si; Pathian ton lai kha ka rak tih ngaingai, Sihmanhsehlaw Jesuh
 thi nih a ka thianh cang.

[C2]
   Ka dawt ko, ka dawt ko, A ka dawt hmasa i Kalvary thingcung in a ka
   tlanh cang ca ah.

[V3]
 Sualnak rak ka tem hmanhseh ka luat cang, Mitcaw ka si nain ceu ka hmu
 cang; Rak thi hmanhning Khrih chungah ka nung cang, Daihnak a ka pekmi
 vawlei cung chim awkah.

[C3]
   Ka dawt ko, ka dawt ko, A ka dawt hmasa i Kalvary thingcung in a ka
   tlanh cang ca ah.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
</song>